          "Start of Semester",
          "Each row represents an enrollment. \n\nCourse data was collected across a 10 year period. Authors only consider courses of lecture type.\n\nData between 2008 and 2015 was used for training, 2016 for validation and 2017 for testing purposes. \n\nWeight decay and Dropout layers have been used.",
          "LSTM",
          "Holdout Method",
          "{Accuracy: 0.8805 - Model 2 on B Threshold, F1-Score: 0.6024 - Model 2 on A Threshold}",
          "The paper is relatively complex as it uses an LSTM model to predict a learner’s grade on a course. ",
          "Only LSTMs are considered.\n\nRequires additional validation (other than backtesting) before deployment.  \n\nResults are somewhat biased because of Grade Letter Aggregation."
        ],
