    {
      "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8005-a69d-d7913c7f3a78",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors test their model by using tests of grade prediction and the recovery of pre-requisites as articulated by the university. On a third step, authors compare behavior of students in the semester preceding a course versus a simulated version where students would have taken the recommended courses. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8005-a69d-d7913c7f3a78",
        "parent": {
